headline: California American Water and Assemblywoman Soria Partner to Support Madera County Food Bank
summary: MADERA, Calif., November 13, 2025--California American Water, in partnership with Assemblywoman Esmeralda Soria, presented a $2,500 donation to the Madera County Food Bank as part of the annual Operation Gobble campaign.

headline: American Water Works Stock Outlook: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish?
summary: American Water Works has underperformed the broader market over the past year, and analysts are cautious about the stock’s prospects.
